---
unit: 6
unitTitle: So & Neither
title: "Unit 6: So & Neither — iCALL Suite"
description: "Learn how to use 'so' and 'neither' to agree with positive and negative statements using the correct auxiliary verb."
objectives:
  - Understand when to use 'so' (positive) and 'neither' (negative) in responses
  - Select the correct auxiliary verb to match the original statement
  - Produce grammatically correct so/neither responses
pageScripts:
